::Prowl/Kluster::

Prowl catches the worried looks in Iron Raptor's optics, understanding what 
she was worried about. His eyes glance over her, knowing that she was 
probably still mad at him for his comment. He takes a few steps toward her, 
thinking over her question.

"Last time I saw it, it was almost to the point of falling apart," he says, 
attempting to put an arm around her.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster looks Iron Raptor over as she turns around. He could tell that Prowl 
liked her, but he had a slight crush on her as well. His eyes take in her 
form as she turns to him, shaking out of his trance as he hears her words. He 
walks over to a console, tapping a few keys.

"The scanners report that the hull has caved in," he says after a few 
seconds, "It's falling apart."
